{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Class","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"}],"title":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B31ThemeTagComponentTokensProviderC","symbolKind":"class"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of tag"}]},{"text":" for ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tag"}]},{"text":" objects like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTag"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllTagComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"TagComponentTokens"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tags"}]},{"text":" through any ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags"}]},{"text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of dimensions (","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":") ,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":") , sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizesSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":")","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and borders (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllTagComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent03TagB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"overview"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for tag component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomTagComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeTagComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ 